{"type": "article", "id": 25708, "title": "蓝色的葡萄酒瓶包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-20T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021308210FvgPezB7RWxhU12.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是巴西的工作室为葡萄酒设计的包装和品牌形象，他们想要突出品牌本身的优雅。酒瓶的外形很普通，采用了天蓝色作为主要颜色，对比近似深蓝色的酒瓶让人觉得清爽。品牌的首字母“V”和“C”被设计成一个类似大写的“A”的符号作为 logo，出现在瓶盖或纸张的水印上，也有印章的感觉，很古典。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130819UoOfSrvMgEpy2n7k.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130820DRWIzdCPmL3MOUGy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130820ypNWagLj0Akth4wB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130821sIgxoQHCKd6J2WlE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}